column5: Visit My WebsiteI finally got out last night for a hour and a half on Sturgeon lake and caught this 5lbs walleye . I also caught a few others but the bite was tough. Fish were caught on a bps 2"  glow in the dark grub tipped with a worm. Cheers jeff
